commit message: Added in some to-do items for the next release.

Updated the engine loader to consider the echo spacing and count (or
calculate the total distance with echoes), and using that to determin
the true minimum and maximum X, Y coordinates.
Added in some padding to the seekbar preference dialog layout.
Added in the ability to change the movement speed.

Updated the ReadMe Mark Down to reflect the work that still needs to be
done.
Fixed the formatting issue in the ReadMe Mark Down
Fixed the mispelling of the world, 'miscellaneous'

Moved the speed seek bar widget minimum and maximum values to private
members of the class.

Update README.md

Added in a notice about the unofficial publication on Google Play.
Turning off  the speed feature; need to add copyright information first.
Added in an About option, and added in some legal information.
